                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-carbon low-nitrogen combustion method applied to fluidized bed boiler",
                    "一种应用于流化床锅炉的低碳低氮燃烧方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a low-carbon low-nitrogen combustion method applied to a fluidized bed boiler, and belongs to the technical field of fluidized bed low-carbon nitrogen reduction. Hydrogen-rich gas fuel is introduced into a primary air inlet and a secondary air inlet of the fluidized bed boiler, specifically, hydrogen-rich alternative fuel is coal pyrolysis gas with hydrogen and methane as main components; the coal pyrolysis gas is used as alternative fuel, so that the consumption of coal is reduced from the source, and carbon dioxide and nitrogen oxide are reduced from the source; in the combustion process, methane and hydrogen have high reducibility, nitric oxide is reduced, so that generation of nitric oxide and generation of carbon dioxide are reduced, the good effect of greatly reducing carbon and nitrogen is achieved, and the method has the advantages of being environmentally friendly, low in economical efficiency and free of equipment transformation."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种应用于流化床锅炉的低碳低氮燃烧方法，属于流化床低碳降氮技术领域，本发明在流化床锅炉一二次风入口通入富氢气体燃料，具体富氢替代燃料为以氢气和甲烷为主要成分的煤热解气，本发明采用煤热解气作为替代燃料，不仅在源头减少煤的消耗量，而且实现从源头上减少二氧化碳和氮氧化物；在燃烧过程中甲烷和氢气具有强还原性，还原一氧化氮从而减少氮氧化物的产生同时减少二氧化碳的产生，达到大幅减碳降氮的良好效果，具有绿色环保、经济性低和不需要改造设备的优点。"
                }
            ]
        }
